      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">What is career coaching?</h2>
      <p>Career coaching is structured, 1-on-1 professional guidance that helps you identify your strongest next move, position yourself for it, and execute a job search that converts. At Askia, it is not generic accountability or motivation. It is a targeted system built around your real experience, the roles you should be targeting, and the gaps between where you are and where the market needs to see you.</p>
      <p>The result is a job search that runs on signal — cleaner applications, better interview conversations, and stronger offers — rather than volume and hope.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content-panel">
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-glow">Who is career coaching for?</h2>
