        <li>Mid-to-senior professionals in tech, business, finance, or healthcare</li>
        <li>Professionals targeting their next step up in level, scope, or compensation</li>
        <li>People applying consistently but not getting traction — interviews, offers, or both</li>
        <li>Anyone who knows they are underselling their experience</li>
        <li>Professionals targeting roles between $100K and $350K</li>
        <li>Leaders aiming for Director, VP, or C-suite transitions</li>
